{"tid":1180174,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)最高危機 希魔撞正殺人狂","createTime":"2019-05-31T15:36:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-31T18:59:55.000Z","uid":29160,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"2c67522d5486671c0a90f1a69ab0c1c11a0469ef","tid":1180174,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T15:36:57.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">睇清楚時間幾點播</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=RSiYdbgXC1SHA4i8VFLgbaf05AUSLZuDOcHdeYvmXak%3D&h=419af552\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 關ADBLOCK先睇到V台 順便開返個FLASHPLAYER<br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=RSiYdbgXC1SHA4i8VFLgbaf05AUSLZuDOcHdeYvmXak%3D&h=d7a5b8cb\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有OKRU睇<br />\n<a href=\"https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.wixstatic.com%2Fmedia%2Fd8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg&d=RSiYdbgXC1SHA4i8VFLgbaf05AUSLZuDOcHdeYvmXak%3D&h=ba9ea356\" target=\"_blank\">https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg</a> &lt; GOOGLE睇唔到解決方法好似係 BY伯爵<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/8/83/ExecutiveDecision_poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F8%2F83%2FExecutiveDecision_poster.jpg&h=3f3df4c2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.一架載滿400名乘客的波音747從希臘雅典起飛前往美國華盛頓首府的途中，被一群由阿拉伯人納吉&middot;哈森帶領的恐怖份子挾持，要求美國釋放他們的首腦艾爾&middot;沙耶&middot;亞法，否則將在華盛頓上空引爆機上的毒氣彈，摧毀美國東岸超過四千萬條人命..<br />\n<br />\n2.在二次大戰期間德占區的法國，外號「猶太獵人」（The Jew Hunter）的親衛隊上校漢斯&middot;蘭達（Hans Landa，克里斯多夫&middot;華茲飾）在一位法國奶農皮埃爾&middot;拉帕提（Perrier LaPadite）的家中審問他。拉帕提為了家人的安全供認了猶太裔的德瑞芙斯（Dreyfus）一家就藏在他家的地板下。蘭達讓親衛隊士兵隔著地板掃射殺害了這一家人，但少女蘇珊娜（Shosanna，梅蘭妮&middot;羅蘭飾）僥倖逃脫<br />\n<br />\n11 40PM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=RSiYdbgXC1SHA4i8VFLgbaf05AUSLZuDOcHdeYvmXak%3D&h=a44bb85e\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=RSiYdbgXC1SHA4i8VFLgbaf05AUSLZuDOcHdeYvmXak%3D&h=1272c2e3\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb6ce8f645f4071ef28a94cdc55fe4990a54ca71","tid":1180174,"uid":29160,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T15:37:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/8/81/Inglourious_Basterds_Poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F8%2F81%2FInglourious_Basterds_Poster.jpg&h=90efad21&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"375bada021f6633c03602a49949440b0527d2bf1","tid":1180174,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T16:14:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4491bbf7a7541